        <h2>Perforated Duodenal Ulcer</h2>
        <p>Peptic ulcer disease is generally a medical condition where advances in diagnosis and treatment have made surgical intervention only reserved for its complications. Perforated duodenal ulcers remain a feared and relatively common complication.</p>
